  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dc0 \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db4\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1 \u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db8 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The date of appointing a new president will be fixed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It has been decided in the party leaders' meeting held this morning that the acceptance of nominations for the appointment of a new president will be done on the 19th.",
        "Accordingly, it has been decided to hold the poll to elect the new president on the 20th.",
        "The resignation letter of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa will be submitted to the Parliament after the Parliament is convened tomorrow at 10 am."
      ],
